Class CareerStaffDbMgr

java.lang.Object
CareerStaffDbMgr
public class CareerStaffDbMgr extends Object
Manages the in-memory list and CSV persistence of CareerStaff records. This class is implemented as a singleton and is responsible for importing career staff data from a CSV file at startup and exporting the current state back to the CSV file when requested. It also provides helper methods for searching, adding, removing, sorting, and filtering career staff.
